   534	
   535	## §4 — Cache layout
   536	
   537	**Primary path:**
   538	
   539	```
   540	<dirs::cache_dir>()/fathomdb/embedders/<model-sha-prefix>/<file>
   541	```
   542	
   543	- `<dirs::cache_dir>()` resolves per the `dirs` crate's platform table:
   544	  - Linux: `$XDG_CACHE_HOME` or `~/.cache`
   545	  - macOS: `~/Library/Caches`
   546	  - Windows: `{FOLDERID_LocalAppData}` (typically `C:\Users\<u>\AppData\Local`)
   547	- `<model-sha-prefix>` = first 12 hex chars of
   548	  `sha256("<repo>@<revision>")`. For the pinned 0.7.1 identity
   549	  (`BAAI/bge-small-en-v1.5@5c38ec7c...`) this resolves to a single
   550	  deterministic prefix that EU-3 may hard-code as a test constant. Using
   551	  a content-addressed prefix means revision bumps land in a different
   552	  cache directory cleanly, without overwriting the older one.
   553	- `<file>` is the bare filename from §1 (`config.json`,
   554	  `tokenizer.json`, `model.safetensors`).
   555	
   556	**HF-hub compat probe (best-effort, read-only).** Before issuing any
   557	network request, the loader checks:
   558	
   559	```
   560	$HF_HOME/hub/models--<repo-encoded>/snapshots/<revision>/<file>
   561	```
   562	
   563	where `<repo-encoded>` is the standard HF-hub flattening (`/` → `--`,
   564	e.g. `models--BAAI--bge-small-en-v1.5`) and `$HF_HOME` defaults to
   565	`~/.cache/huggingface` if unset.
   566	
   567	If the file exists AND its sha256 matches the pinned constant, the
   568	loader copies (or, on POSIX, hard-links — same filesystem only) the file
   569	into the fathomdb cache. The HF-hub cache is **never written to** by
   570	fathomdb; the probe is strictly read-only.
   571	
   572	A `DefaultEmbedderCacheHit { cache_path, sha256_verified: true }` event
   573	is emitted in this case (see §7).
   574	
   575	**Per-platform expansion examples** (illustrative, for cross-cite from
   576	EU-3 tests):
   577	
   578	| platform | resolved cache path                                                                |
   579	|----------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
   580	| Linux    | `~/.cache/fathomdb/embedders/<prefix>/model.safetensors`                           |
   581	| macOS    | `~/Library/Caches/fathomdb/embedders/<prefix>/model.safetensors`                   |
   582	| Windows  | `%LOCALAPPDATA%\fathomdb\embedders\<prefix>\model.safetensors`                     |
   583	
