## Verdict: PASS

No findings.

**What passed on inspection**

- `git diff --name-only 4beca5b..10a0e24` is docs-only: `dev/architecture.md`, `dev/design/embedder-decision.md`, `dev/adr/ADR-0.6.0-default-embedder.md`, `dev/notes/0.7.0-vector-cost-research.md`, and `dev/plans/runs/0.7.2-PR-1-output.json`. The follow-up commit `10a0e24` adds only the closure artifact.
- The shipped-embedder claims line up with repo truth: default embedder is `BAAI/bge-small-en-v1.5`, 384d, mean-centering-required in engine, `TOP_K_BIT_CANDIDATES = 192`, `MEAN_VEC_PIN_THRESHOLD = 256`, and first-use sha256-verified loading via a thin `ureq` blocking client, not `hf-hub` (`dev/architecture.md:46,70-73,483-487`; `dev/design/embedder.md:455-467,535-582`; `src/rust/crates/fathomdb-embedder/src/loader.rs:7-16,49-78,311-325,434-442`; `src/rust/crates/fathomdb-engine/src/lib.rs:881-885,2893,2900`; `src/rust/crates/fathomdb-embedder/src/candle_bge.rs:8-10`).
- The cache-root correction matches `embedder.md §4` exactly: `<dirs::cache_dir>()/fathomdb/embedders/<model-sha-prefix>/...` (`dev/architecture.md:271-275`; `dev/design/embedder.md:535-582`; `src/rust/crates/fathomdb-embedder/src/loader.rs:11,440-442`).
- The recall-floor edits stay descriptive and honest: 0.90 held, `0.828/~0.83` is called out as artifact, corrected ANN-fidelity recall@10 is `0.937` with `R − 2σ => 0.91`, and EU-8 IR `0.571` remains a separate ceiling (`dev/design/embedder-decision.md:390-422`; `dev/adr/ADR-0.6.0-default-embedder.md:210-218`; `dev/adr/ADR-0.7.0-vector-binary-quant.md:136-176`; `dev/plans/runs/0.7.2-PR-2bc-decision.md:1-18,212-226`).
- The intentional historical/additive constraints were preserved: D2’s sentence body remains frozen with only an appended resolution pointer, and the research-note re-status is additive while explicitly stating Matryoshka did not ship (`dev/adr/ADR-0.6.0-default-embedder.md:196-199`; `dev/notes/0.7.0-vector-cost-research.md:187-204`).
- Nothing in the landed docs claims `v0.7.1` is tagged or released. The ADR explicitly says “not yet tagged,” workspace versions remain `0.7.0`, and `git tag --list 'v0.7.1'` is empty (`dev/adr/ADR-0.6.0-default-embedder.md:217-218`; `Cargo.toml:28,48-53`).

